	title = {Shape {Designer} for {ShEx} and {SHACL} {Constraints}},
	abstract = {We present Shape Designer, a graphical tool for building SHACL or ShEx constraints for an existing RDF dataset. Shape Designer allows to automatically extract complex constraints that are satisﬁed by the data. Its integrated shape editor and validator allow expert users to combine and modify these constraints in order to build an arbitrarily complex ShEx or SHACL schema.},
